{"tid":559741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再多4.7萬單程證 本港人口突破740萬","createTime":"2018-02-13T12:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T14:42:02.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dedc9c6e3a0bff7813bbc0e7e00f2ce55e2045b9","tid":559741,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/203119_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F203119_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8a1959cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/203122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F203122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7c13f916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府統計處公佈，2017年底本港人口的臨時數字為7,409,800人，與之前一年比較，增加了32,700人，增長率為0.4%。2016年底至2017年底的人口自然增長為1萬人，其中出生人數56,600人，死亡人數46,600人。在同期內，淨遷移人數為22,600人，其中有多達47,000單程證持有人的移入，24,300人為其他香港居民的淨移出。<br />\n<br />\n根據統計處的臨時數字，2017底總人口常住居民佔7,182,600人，流動居民佔227,200人。2017年年中人口修訂數字為7,391,700人。常住居民的數字修訂為7,172,800人，流動居民的數字修訂為218,900人。2016年年中至2017年年中的人口增長率亦修訂為0.8%。家庭住戶數目為2,540,700，家庭住戶平均人數為2.8。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180213/57829003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180213%2F57829003&d=juZNQ8TWd%2FZKTWwpyWEy8v9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=2a90044e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180213%2F57829003&h=d4be2287\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180213/57829003</a>"},{"pid":"9e058a02d8264e421bec7653003e18730cae1af8","tid":559741,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:32:03